shaoli mitra ( alternative spelling shaonli mitra ) is a bengali theatre and film actress . she played the role of bangabala in ritwik ghatak 's jukti takko aar gappo . she is the daughter of sombhu mitra and tripti mitra , who were also theatre personalities . in 2011 , she was a chairperson of rabindra shardhoshato janmabarsha udjapon samiti .